The paper deals with the analysis of the downlink coverage probability of a Poisson network with double shadowed fading, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also uses mathematical tools such as Gaussian-Hermit quadrature, which is related to game theory (cs.GT) and simulation (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper uses analytical tractability, which is related to mathematical analysis (cs.MA).
